==古生物學==
===體格===
與祖先及更衍化的近緣物種相比之下，查摩西斯龍外型較為粗壯且身材圓潤。因為有發現幼體化石，已對其亞種個體發育有相對多的了解。諾普查指出[[哈采格|哈采格]]地區的動物體型明顯小於其他地方的親戚，顯示牠們患有島嶼侏儒症。<ref name="weishampeletal03" />兩種查摩西斯龍的化石發現於{{link-en|聖佩楚層|Sânpetru Formation}}、{{link-en|色貝斯層|Sebeș Formation}}、{{link-en|丹瑟斯裘拉層|Densuş-Ciula Formation}}，皆涵蓋於[[哈采格島|哈采格島]]的範圍。<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Godefroit |first1=Pascal |last2=Codrea |first2=Vlad |last3=Weishampel |first3=David B. |title=Osteology of Zalmoxes shqiperorum (Dinosauria, Ornithopoda), based on new specimens from the Upper Cretaceous of Nalat-Vad (Romania) |journal=Geodiversitas |date=30 September 2009 |volume=31 |issue=3 |pages=525–553 |doi=10.5252/g2009n3a3 |s2cid=131476195 |url=http://sciencepress.mnhn.fr/en/periodiques/geodiversitas/31/3/osteologie-de-zalmoxes-shqiperorum-dinosauria-ornithopoda-d-apres-de-nouveaux-specimens-du-cretace-superieur-de-nalat-vad-roumanie |access-date=30 October 2020}}</ref>

===食性===
2003年的研究指出查摩西斯龍的食物可能包括堅韌的植物纖維如{{link-en|芽|Shoot}}、[[木賊|木賊]]、[[被子植物|被子植物]]、[[羊齒植物|羊齒植物]]、[[蕨類|蕨類]]。<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Weishampel |first1=Dave |last2=Csiki-Sava |first2=Zoltan |last3=Norman |first3=David |title=Osteology and phylogeny of Zalmoxes (n. g.), an unusual Euornithopod dinosaur from the latest Cretaceous of Romania |journal=Journal of Systematic Palaeontology |date=January 2003 |volume=1 |issue=2 |pages=65–123 |doi=10.1017/S1477201903001032 |s2cid=86339025 |url=https://www.researchgate.net/publication/248623465 |access-date=24 February 2021}}</ref>

